{"tha-ap76:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap76:0.2":"Nagasamalavagga ","tha-ap76:0.3":"Bhisaluvadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap76:1.1":"“Kananam vanamogayha, ","tha-ap76:1.2":"vasami vipine aham; ","tha-ap76:1.3":"Vipassim addasam buddham, ","tha-ap76:1.4":"ahutinam patiggaham. ","tha-ap76:2.1":"Bhisaluvanca padasim, ","tha-ap76:2.2":"udakam hatthadhovanam; ","tha-ap76:2.3":"Vanditva sirasa pade, ","tha-ap76:2.4":"pakkami uttaramukho. ","tha-ap76:3.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap76:3.2":"bhisaluvamadam tada; ","tha-ap76:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap76:3.4":"punnakammassidam phalam. ","tha-ap76:4.1":"Ito tatiyake kappe, ","tha-ap76:4.2":"bhisasammatakhattiyo; ","tha-ap76:4.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap76:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap76:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap76:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap76:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap76:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma bhisaluvadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap76:7.1":"Bhisaluvadayakattherassapadanam catuttham. ","tha-ap76:7.2":"Chatthabhanavaram. "}